  <body>
    <segment id="1">

Finally give it rubber !</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="24" relname="list"> 

A synthetic track on Schwedendamm would cost one million marks.</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="24" relname="list">  The bridge over the city canal will also be so expensive.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="24" relname="list">  Renewing the paths on the vineyard costs two million.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="24" relname="list">  The Havellandhalle has cost 5.5 million.</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="24" relname="list">  The new playground in Ost cost 1.5 million.</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="24" relname="list">  The area in front of Kaufhalle Ost is to be redesigned for 1.5 million euros.</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="9" relname="concession">

Comparisons may be a little off.</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="25" relname="span"> But no one should say that there is no money.</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="28" relname="span">  What is most important to those responsible at the moment is being built.</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="27" relname="conjunction">  It&apos;s as simple as that,</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="27" relname="conjunction"> and they call it &quot;politics&quot;.</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="14" relname="evaluation-n">  Never before have track and field athletes from Rathenow and Premnitz won top places at German championships as often as this year.</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="30" relname="span">  They have really earned their tartan.</segment>
    <segment id="15" parent="16" relname="antithesis">

You can run on ash from April to September at most,</segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="31" relname="span"> but at any time on artificial surfaces.</segment>
    <segment id="17" parent="33" relname="list">  The jumping facilities at Schwedendamm are unacceptable.</segment>
    <segment id="18" parent="19" relname="condition"> Whoever finally builds a proper stadium,</segment>
    <segment id="19" parent="32" relname="span"> will be simply keeping up with the times.</segment>
    <segment id="20" parent="35" relname="reason">  School sports also take place at the Jahn-Sportpark. </segment>
    <segment id="21" parent="35" relname="span"> It would be beneficial for children and teenagers.</segment>
    <segment id="22" parent="34" relname="conjunction"> They would be much cleaner after sports,</segment>
    <segment id="23" parent="34" relname="conjunction"> and they would also run better times on rubber.</segment>
<group id="24" type="multinuc" parent="25" relname="evidence" />
